Usage: setHInstColorId [-help] <hInstName> <colorID> [-descendant]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<hInstName>            # Name of the hierarchical instance (string, required)
<colorID>              # color ID from 0 to 29 (int, required, min=0, max=29)
-descendant            # Specifies that the color ID should be applied to the
                       # child/descendant instances as well (bool, optional)